{"tid":1525322,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對唔住各位，我真心有啲驚","createTime":"2019-08-31T22:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:51:35.000Z","uid":262211,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce2be62e9eacc86781d67a692e02d931b219126","tid":1525322,"uid":262211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:18:15.000Z","msg":"我只係一個中學生，屋企人全部都藍絲<br />\n但係我都冇理到佢哋，次次有遊行集會我都會出嚟幫手，可能微不足道，但係我知道自己係做緊正確嘅嘢，所以我唔驚被人秋後算帳。 <br />\n但係經過今日太子恐襲， 我真心驚左，我好驚自己有一日無端端咁樣俾人打，我真係有啲動搖啦。<br />\n但係諗下，就算驚有咩辦法呀。如果個個都驚咁邊個願意行出黎？所以今日9月1號唔該大家出一出嚟盡一分力"},{"pid":"0d68d53487a55d4e101be785d61a4211dfbd0c1c","tid":1525322,"uid":50983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:19:58.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n我地無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b84da2a95bf765d8d6beaadbd6bb95a2e13aba1","tid":1525322,"uid":120086,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:20:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbca56ca30bf908ebf02b4a6961899880f650cef","tid":1525322,"uid":262211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d68d53487a55d4e101be785d61a4211dfbd0c1c","tid":1525322,"uid":50983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:19:58.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n我地無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:20:51.000Z","msg":"唉 我人住太子 望到今日咁真係好心痛"},{"pid":"7df55b8c9acd3172fe014d140d45c193bdbb3254","tid":1525322,"uid":248932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:21:11.000Z","msg":"動搖既時候<br />\n望一望後面<br />\n我地撐住你"},{"pid":"ca7400514da9a6f914cf5c86cf58f8ed97e0ea6e","tid":1525322,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T22:21:24.000Z","msg":"twitter網軍<br />\n住得近狗舍同地鐵站可以做哨<br />\n學校有影印就幫人印"},{"pid":"960036cc92e19f5c146537821d67318e09